  "description": "This individual is an undead human of lean, sinew-bare build, with taut amber skin stretched over prominent cheekbones and a narrow jaw. Gray eyes sit deep in the sockets beneath a fixed, cadaverous brow, giving the face a sunken, cavern-worn cast. Black hair grows in sparse, uneven lengths, leaving patches of scalp exposed and emphasizing the skull’s contours. The mouth holds a permanent, desiccated set, and the hands show long, rigid fingers suited to patient, unrelenting grasp.",
